---
title: Saucy Maple-Mustard Pork Chops with Cheesy Mash, Carrots and Peas
description: Perfectly seasoned pork chops are smothered in a maple-mustard sauce for tonight's feast but the best part is the cheesy mash! Paired with a simple roasted buttered veggie pouch, this one is sure to hit all the right notes.
